```

👉 Constructor → jab node banega tab value assign hogi

---

### Base Case

```cpp
if (root == NULL)
    return -1;
```

👉 Agar node exist nahi karta → height = -1 (edges definition)

---

### Recursive Calls

```cpp
int leftHeight = height(root->left);
```

👉 Left subtree ki height nikaal rahe ho

```cpp
int rightHeight = height(root->right);
```

👉 Right subtree ki height nikaal rahe ho

---

### Final Answer

```cpp
return max(leftHeight, rightHeight) + 1;
```

👉 Jo side zyada deep hai usko lo + current node add karo

